Description_lang: Healing done to allies is increased by ${$s1}.1% while their health percentage is lower than your own.

description_blz.en_US: Healing done to allies is increased by 33.5% while their health percentage is lower than your own.
description_blz.es_MX: La sanación realizada a los aliados aumenta un 33.5% cuando su porcentaje de salud es menor al tuyo.
description_blz.pt_BR: Cura realizada em aliados aumenta em 33,5% quando a porcentagem de pontos de vida deles é inferior à sua.
description_blz.de_DE: Die bei Verbündeten hervorgerufene Heilung ist um 33,5% erhöht, solange deren prozentuale Gesundheit niedriger ist als die Eure.
description_blz.en_GB: Healing done to allies is increased by 33.5% while their health percentage is lower than your own.
description_blz.es_ES: La sanación realizada a los aliados aumenta un 33,5% mientras su porcentaje de salud sea menor que el tuyo.
description_blz.fr_FR: Les soins prodigués aux personnages alliés sont augmentés de 33,5% si leur pourcentage de points de vie restants est inférieur au vôtre.
description_blz.it_IT: Le cure fornite agli alleati aumentano del 33,5% quando la loro salute in percentuale è inferiore alla tua.
description_blz.ru_RU: Вы восполняете союзникам на 33,5% больше здоровья, если их уровень здоровья ниже вашего.
description_blz.ko_KR: 대상 아군의 생명력 비율이 자신보다 낮을 경우, 아군에 대한 치유량이 33.5%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 當盟友的生命力百分比低於你自身的生命力百分比時，對盟友的治療量提高33.5%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 当盟友的生命值百分比低于你时，你对其造成的治疗量提高33.5%。
